ard rapidity.\nThese measurements also significantly extend the $\\mathrm{J}/\\psi$ $p_{\\rm T}$\nreach and supersede previously published results. A comparison with ALICE\nmeasurements in pp collisions at $\\sqrt{s} = 2.76$, 7, 8, and 13 TeV is\npresented and the energy dependence of quarkonium production cross sections is\ndiscussed. Finally, the results are compared with the predictions from several\nproduction models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2021 16:20:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2023 16:39:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
