hough the reconnecting coronal current\nsheets are highly structured, they remain quasi-two-dimensional and the\nmagnetic energy release occurs systematically, rather than stochastically,\nthrough the volume of reconnecting magnetic flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2021 17:57:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Dec 2021 15:53:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-09"}
