ragmented space of\nrobotic comprehension algorithms through the mechanism of Situational Graph\n(S-Graph), a generalization of the well-known scene graph. Therefore, we\nfinally shape our vision for the future of robotic Situational Awareness by\ndiscussing interesting recent research directions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 09:00:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Oct 2021 12:40:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 13:57:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 08:21:53 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 16:14:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
