aining parameter values are categorized according to the performance\ncharacteristics. The condition Higher-the-better is used for parameters like\nFWC and CTE whereas condition Lower-the-better is applied for parameters, such\nas dark current, linearity error and DSNU.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 10:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
