ode to cease transmissions\nonce the exact average of the initial quantized values has been reached (in\norder to preserve its battery energy). Then, we present upper bounds on (i) the\nnumber of transmissions and computations each node has to perform during the\nexecution of the algorithm, and (ii) the memory and energy requirements of each\nnode in order for the algorithm to be executed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 12:48:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
