n of our generator, and the\ndiscriminability of the synthesis also demonstrates the strength of our\ndiscriminator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 13:13:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
